<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Influencer and Collaboration Agreement</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #000; padding: 60px 80px; background: white; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #000; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .document-title { font-size: 22pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .date { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f8f8; border: 2px solid #333; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 200px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { flex: 1; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section-content { text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        strong { font-weight: bold; }
        .form-row { margin-top: 30px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .form-label { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .form-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-height: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .signature-section { margin-top: 40px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header"><div class="document-title">INFLUENCER & COLLABORATION AGREEMENT</div></div>
    <div class="date">Effective Date: {{date}}</div>
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Brand Information</h3>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Brand:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Contact:</div><div class="info-value">{{Email}} | {{Phone}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Social Media:</div><div class="info-value">{{SocialLinks}}</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content">
            This Influencer and Collaboration Agreement ("Agreement") is between <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> ("Brand") and the individual or entity signing below ("Influencer").
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. SCOPE OF COLLABORATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Influencer agrees to create and publish content promoting Brand's products, services, or events as outlined in the Campaign Brief. Deliverables include [number and type of posts, stories, videos, etc.].
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. CONTENT REQUIREMENTS</div>
        <ul>
            <li>Content must align with Brand's values and aesthetic</li>
            <li>Include required hashtags, handles, and disclosure statements (e.g., #ad, #sponsored)</li>
            <li>Submit content for Brand approval before posting (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Post on agreed-upon dates and times</li>
            <li>Comply with FTC guidelines and platform policies</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. COMPENSATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            In exchange for services, Brand will provide: [monetary payment, free products, services, event access, commission/affiliate structure, etc.]. Payment will be made [upon completion, within 30 days, etc.] via [payment method].
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. CONTENT OWNERSHIP AND USAGE RIGHTS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Influencer retains ownership of content but grants Brand a perpetual, worldwide, royalty-free license to use, reproduce, and distribute the content for marketing purposes across all channels.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. FTC COMPLIANCE AND DISCLOSURES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Influencer must clearly disclose the partnership using #ad, #sponsored, or similar language in accordance with FTC guidelines. Failure to comply may result in termination and financial penalties.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. EXCLUSIVITY AND NON-COMPETE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            During the campaign period and for [time period] after, Influencer will not promote competing brands in the [industry/category] without Brand's written consent.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. TERMINATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Either party may terminate this Agreement with [notice period] written notice. Brand may terminate immediately if Influencer violates terms or engages in behavior that damages Brand's reputation.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. CONFIDENTIALITY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Influencer agrees to keep campaign details, compensation, and Brand strategies confidential unless disclosure is required by law or agreed upon by Brand.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">9. GOVERNING LAW</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This Agreement is governed by the laws of <strong>{{Jurisdiction}}</strong>.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Brand:</div><div class="form-line">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Authorized Signature:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Date:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row" style="margin-top: 50px;"><div class="form-label">Influencer Name:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Influencer Signature:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Date:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>